Class UnresolvedEntityException

  • Object
    • Throwable
      • Exception
        • UnresolvedEntityException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class UnresolvedEntityException
extends Exception
    UnresolvedEntityException is an exception class generated during persist operations when a field is not of type CascadeType.Create for create operations and is unmanaged.
